---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Header />
  <div class="container pt-[225px] pb-[67px]">
    <h1 class="main-title">About</h1>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col max-w-[674px] font-text-content font-normal gap-6 mt-[86px] leading-[24px]"
    >
      <p class="">
        As a Creative Director, I generate innovative business ideas, design
        projects, and oversee their execution. Whether directing promotional
        videos or capturing the essence on set as a cameraman, I bring creative
        visions to life. As a specialist in brand development, I provide
        groundbreaking solutions that lead to significant successes.
      </p>

      <p class="">
        My mission is to craft the DNA of brands through MVP (Mission, Value,
        Purpose) development, ensuring that the core essence of the brand
        resonates with customers. Additionally, I focus on designing user
        behaviors with an eye towards the future of DAOs (Decentralized
        Autonomous Organizations).
      </p>

      <p class="">
        In my role, I bridge the gap between creativity and strategy,
        transforming concepts into impactful realities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Button content="Contact" href="/contact/" className="mr-auto mt-7" />
    <h2 class="text-[40px] mt-[120px] font-title">KOHEI HARADA</h2>
    <p class="leading-[24px] font-text-content mt-6">
      Creative Factory <br />
      WIT inc. (Japan) CEO / WIT B.V. <br />
      (Netherlands) CEO
    </p>
  </div>
  <section class="main-sections">
    <article class="main-sections__item main-sections__item--main-sub z-10">
      <div class="container h-full flex-grow">
        <div class="flex flex-col h-full justify-center flex-grow">
          <h2 class="font-title uppercase text-[80px] leading-[80px] mb-6">
            Office
          </h2>
          <Button content="View" className="w-max" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article
        class="main-sections__item main-sections__item--footer overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div class="container h-full flex-grow">
          <div class="flex flex-col h-full justify-center flex-grow">
            <h2
              class="font-title uppercase text-[80px] leading-[80px] mb-6 text-white"
            >
              Future
            </h2>
            <Button content="View" className="w-max" invert />
            <div class="box" id="box1"></div>
            <div class="box" id="box2"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
<style lang="scss">
  .main-sections__item--main-sub {
    background-image: url(../images/office.webp);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
</style>
